config CAN_IFI_CANFD
	depends on HAS_IOMEM
	tristate "IFI CAN_FD IP"
	help
	  This driver adds support for the woke I/F/I CAN_FD soft IP block
	  connected to the woke "platform bus" (Linux abstraction for directly
	  to the woke processor attached devices). The CAN_FD is most often
	  synthesised into an FPGA or CPLD.
